/*!
    \title \QDesSup
    \page qtqmldesignsupport-index.html
    \brief Provides a set of types to allow registering and referencing objects in QML

    The \QDesSup provides support for design tooling with a set of types for
    registering and referencing objects in QML. Objects are identified with a key string at
    registration and reference types can use these keys to get references to the registered objects.
    The idea is to allow clean separation between UI code and business logic, particularly in cases
    where UI code is automatically generated with some tool and developers are not expected to
    manually modify it. The \QDesSup module provides both a
    \l{\QDesSup QML Types}{QML API} and a
    \l{\QDesSup C++ Classes}{C++ API} for referencing registered objects.
    The object registration is only available as \l{\QDesSup QML Types}{QML API}.

    \section1 Using the Module

    \section2 QML API

    \include {module-use.qdocinc} {using the qml api} {QtQml.DesignSupport}

    The \l{\QDesSup QML Types}{QML API} of \QDesSup module
    provides the types required for registering QML objects and referencing registered QML objects.

    \section2 C++ API

    \include {module-use.qdocinc} {using the c++ api}

    The \l{\QDesSup C++ Classes}{C++ API} of \QDesSup
    module provides the classes required for referencing registered QML objects.

    \section3 Building with CMake

    \include {module-use.qdocinc} {building with cmake} {QmlDesignSupport}

    \section3 Building with qmake

    \include {module-use.qdocinc} {building_with_qmake} {qmldesignsupport}

    \section1 API Reference

    \list
        \li \l {\QDesSup C++ Classes} {C++ Classes}
        \li \l {\QDesSup QML Types} {QML Types}
    \endlist

    \section1 Licenses and Attributions

    \QDesSup is available under commercial licenses from \l{The Qt Company}.
    In addition, it is available under the
    \l{GNU Lesser General Public License, version 3}, or
    the \l{GNU General Public License, version 2}.
    See \l{Qt Licensing} for further details.
*/

/*!
    \qmlmodule QtQml.DesignSupport
    \title \QDesSup QML Module
    \ingroup qmlmodules
    \brief QML types for \QDesSup API
    \since 6.12

    The \QDesSup functionality can be accessed via these QML types.
*/

/*!
    \module QtQmlDesignSupport
    \qtcmakepackage QmlDesignSupport
    \qtvariable qmldesignsupport
    \title \QDesSup Module
    \since 6.12

    \brief C++ classes for the \QDesSup API.
*/

/*!
    \title \QDesSup QML Types
    \group qmldesignsupport_qml

    \brief QML types for the \QDesSup API.

    The \QDesSup functionality can be accessed via these QML types.
*/

/*!
    \title \QDesSup C++ Classes
    \group qmldesignsupport

    \brief C++ classes for the \QDesSup API.

    The \QDesSup functionality can be accessed via these C++ classes.
*/
